node.text:
Hey all! So if you didn’t hear, IG has made an announcement that they are going to lean toward “video and entertainment” going forward. (Aka  wanna be Tiktok) IG has been the primary platform for artists for years but  we have all felt the shift of their statement and our work is being suppressed on this platform. It’s unfortunate, and it’s heart breaking because a lot of our livelihoods depend on our work being seen. So please support your favorite creators where you can. Be it here, or any platform you are active in. Thank you guys for supporting us. ❤️

.
.

.
.
